title: What is Dookey Dash? Who can play?
description:
Dookey Dash is a skill-based mint playable like an endless runner — a category of game where you attempt to go as far as possible as the game progresses in difficulty. Your mission: get in the sewer to dodge and break through obstacles as you pick up items called fragments.

As long as you have a Sewer Pass, you can play Dookey Dash at https://mdvmm.xyz from January 19, 2023 to February 8, 2023.

title: What is a Sewer Pass?
description: A Sewer Pass is an NFT that acts as your ticket to play Dookey Dash.

title: Ok, I’m in. How do I get a Sewer Pass?
description: Sewer Passes can be claimed only by BAYC and MAYC holders. If you don't have a BAYC or MAYC NFT, you can't claim a Sewer Pass, but you can get/buy one from a Sewer Pass holder.
